OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1782280079
OL,3,CResidents evacuated after lightning
OL,4,Cstrike causes house fire
OL,6,FMultiple households in Bristol were
OL,7,Fevacuated by fire crews after
OL,8,Flightning struck a home in Emersons
OL,9,FGreen.
OL,11,FA storm hit the city on the evening of
OL,12,FMonday 22 June, causing a house fire
OL,13,Fon Wadham Grove just before 6.00pm.
OL,15,FCrews from Kingswood, Temple,
OL,16,FSouthmead, Patchway and Portishead
OL,17,Ffire stations found the building well
OL,18,Falight and neighbours had to evacuate
OL,19,Ftheir properties.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
