PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1782280079
OL,3,CResidents evacuated after lightning
OL,4,Cstrike causes house fire
OL,6,FFirefighters have been inspecting the
OL,7,Fsite this morning, Tuesday 23 June, to
OL,8,Fmake sure the fire is completely
OL,9,Fextinguished.
OL,11,FAvon Fire and Rescue Service said:"At
OL,12,F5:55pm on 22 June, crews from
OL,13,FKingswood, Temple, Southmead, Patchway
OL,14,Fand Portishead fire stations were
OL,15,Fcalled to reports of a house fire on
OL,16,FWadham Grove, Emersons Green.
OL,26,@sD@cOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1782280079
OL,3,CResidents evacuated after lightning
OL,4,Cstrike causes house fire
OL,6,F"Upon arrival, crews found the house
OL,7,Fwell alight with significant damage.
OL,8,FFirefighters quickly brought the fire
OL,9,Funder control and extinguished it
OL,10,Fusing high-pressure hose reels and
OL,11,Fwater jets.
OL,13,F"They remained on scene to dampen down
OL,14,Fthe area and used thermal imaging
OL,15,Fcameras and gas monitors to check for
OL,16,Fany hotspots.
OL,18,F"Crews also isolated electricity at
OL,19,Fthe property and in nearby affected
OL,20,Fhomes. All affected properties were
OL,21,Fevacuated.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1782280079
OL,3,CResidents evacuated after lightning
OL,4,Cstrike causes house fire
OL,6,F"Once the situation was safe and the
OL,7,Ffire was out, crews were able to leave
OL,8,Fthe scene. They then did two more
OL,9,Froutine reinspections, one in the
OL,10,Fearly hours of this morning and
OL,11,Fanother at around 7am, to ensure
OL,12,Feverything was still safe.
OL,14,F"One person was injured near the
OL,15,Fscene, unrelated to the incident and
OL,16,Fwas handed over to the ambulance
OL,17,Fservice.
OL,19,F"The cause of the fire is accidental
OL,20,Fand thought to be from a lightning
OL,21,Fstrike."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
