FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1782280079
OL,3,CResidents evacuated after lightning
OL,4,Cstrike causes house fire
OL,6,FHundreds of households on the
OL,7,Foutskirts of the city experienced a
OL,8,Fpower cut during the storm and Bristol
OL,9,FAirport was forced to suspend its
OL,10,Fflights.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, businesses in Bath and
OL,13,FGlastonbury are dealing with the
OL,14,Faftermath of flash flooding, with
OL,15,Ftemperatures expected to rise well
OL,16,Fover 30 degrees this week.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
